GabeOS Live Environment – UEFI Mode
====================================
This system requires UEFI firmware with GPT partitioning.
Legacy BIOS / CSM boot is NOT supported.

If you are installing GabeOS, ensure your target disk uses a
GPT partition table with an EFI System Partition (ESP, FAT32,
minimum 512 MiB) mounted at /boot/efi.

GRUB (x86_64-efi) will be installed as the bootloader.
